</p>
<p> In this report, the Special Rapporteur focuses in particular on topics related to the 
recognition and protection of land and natural resources, including: the cadastral survey 
programme and the extractive and agricultural industries; access to justice, evictions and 
social protest; and the social and economic situation of indigenous peoples, including their 
education, health and development. 
</p>
<p> </p>

